To recompile this puppy:
    - install on debian:
      - libx11-dev
      - libxft-dev
      - libxext-dev
    - install on fedora:
      - libX11-devel
      - libXft-devel

    - download the latest release from st.suckless.org
    - copy config.h into there
    - run `make clean install`
    - have fun with the compiled binary at /usr/local/bin/